---
@META
dir: src/store
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 1
stack: Zustand 4, TypeScript

@EXPORTS
user-store.ts: useUserStore — Zustand store with localStorage persistence for client-side user state

@FUNCTIONS
setUser(user:{userId,username,email,avatar?}) → void
  purpose: set authenticated user identity
  side-effects: cache (localStorage via zustand/persist)
  called-by: auth components

addXP(amount:number) → void
  purpose: increment XP & recalculate level (sqrt(xp/100)+1)
  side-effects: cache (localStorage)
  called-by: chapter completion, quiz, project submission

completeLesson(lessonId:string, xpEarned:number) → void
  purpose: mark lesson complete, add XP, prevent duplicate completions
  side-effects: cache (localStorage)
  called-by: chapter page

updateStreak() → void
  purpose: increment/reset daily streak based on lastActiveDate
  side-effects: cache (localStorage)
  called-by: app layout on load

reset() → void
  purpose: clear all user state (logout)
  side-effects: cache (localStorage clear)
  called-by: signout flow

@INTERFACES
UserState: { userId:string|null, username:string|null, email:string|null, avatar:string|null, onboardingCompleted:boolean, userGoal:string|null, experienceLevel:string|null, xp:number, level:number, streak:number, lastActiveDate:string|null, badges:Badge[], progress:UserProgress[] }
Badge: { id:string, name:string, description:string, icon:string, unlockedAt?:Date }
UserProgress: { lessonId:string, completedAt:Date, xpEarned:number }

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: none
external: zustand, zustand/middleware (persist)

@STANDARDS
- persist middleware stores to localStorage key "user-storage"
- Level calculation duplicated from lib/gamification.ts — keep in sync

@WARNINGS
- Client-side state only — NOT source of truth, server DB is authoritative
- calculateLevel duplicated inline — potential drift from lib/gamification.ts
---
